From eb38bfaf9774a3d89b38410590e47cd34ba7762e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Arunpandi Kannan <arunpand@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Sep 2025 09:24:37 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK:CP: wifi: ath12k: Add support for off-channel tx/rx.

Add support to send management packets in off-channel using
remain on channel. Do enable offchannel tx and rx by doing
start vap when remain on channel issued.

Handle the tx status of the off-channel packets.

Signed-off-by: Arunpandi Kannan <arunpand@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c |  94 ++++++++++--
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wmi.c | 207 +++++++++++++++++++++++++-
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wmi.h |  11 +-
 3 files changed, 298 insertions(+), 14 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c b/drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/mac.c
